short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Autoland Phabricator revisions which are ready to land

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Performs checks on a regular basis to automatically land diffs that pass all builds.

Setup:
1) Update the Phabricator URL in the extension options
2) Ensure you are logged into Phabricator
3) Add #autoland to the summary of every diff you want to automatically land
